messages.subject: Old is as Old does...
messages.msgSnippet: Hello all, I don t normally post much, but was delighted to find that I am 158.4 Mercurian years old. Now, that s longevity!  (grin)
messages.messageBody:
Hello all,

I don't normally post much, but was delighted to find that I am 158.4
Mercurian years old.
Now, that's longevity! (grin)
http://www.exploratorium.edu/ronh/age/index.html
I'm only 62 Venusian years old, but somehow, I can't help but think that
Venusians have more fun than Mercurians, so maybe those 62 years are just
more jam-packed...
Enjoy!
HeidiWD
